author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Pluralsight - Anticipate IPO Price Of Class A Common Stock Will Be Between $12.00 And $14.00 Per Share
text:
May 15 (Reuters) - Pluralsight LLC:
* PLURALSIGHT INC - ANTICIPATE INITIAL PUBLIC OFFERING PRICE OF CLASS A COMMON STOCK WILL BE BETWEEN $12.00 AND $14.00 PER SHARE - SEC FILING
* PLURALSIGHT INC SAYS IT HAD PREVIOUSLY EXPECTED IPO PRICED BETWEEN $10 AND $12 PER SHARE - SEC FILING Source text: ( bit.ly/2L0Ifxf ) Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
